266
00:22:06,020 --> 00:22:09,440
They look happy up there. Jiang Zhengxu!

267
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:11,860
Coach, remember to buy movie tickets.

268
00:22:11,860 --> 00:22:14,840
Coach, look at them!

269
00:22:14,840 --> 00:22:16,499
I didn't expect that you are so tall.

270
00:22:16,500 --> 00:22:18,419
I didn't complain that you're short.

271
00:22:18,420 --> 00:22:20,420
