283
00:23:03,250 --> 00:23:07,960
♪  Keeping quiet and missing
you at the same time ♪

284
00:23:07,960 --> 00:23:12,450
♪  I am so near to reach my dreams  ♪

285
00:23:12,450 --> 00:23:19,920
♪  All I need is you to complete me  ♪

286
00:23:19,920 --> 00:23:22,769
♪  Life is fated  ♪

287
00:23:22,770 --> 00:23:27,330
♪ It's hard to speak due to a relationship ♪

288
00:23:27,330 --> 00:23:30,590
♪  Why does it feel like our first meeting  ♪

289
00:23:30,590 --> 00:23:35,630
♪  between the gaps of my vision  ♪

290
00:23:35,630 --> 00:23:38,320
♪  The more I misunderstand, the more I fall for you.  ♪

291
00:23:38,320 --> 00:23:43,400
♪  The answer swings back and forth  ♪

292
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:47,280
♪  It tugged my heartstrings.  ♪

293
00:23:47,280 --> 00:23:55,120
♪  I wonder how far am I apart from you  ♪

294
00:24:02,060 --> 00:24:07,480
Lin Xichi, what kind of a dream was that?

295
00:24:07,480 --> 00:24:10,560
What are you even thinking?

296
00:24:10,560 --> 00:24:13,739
Did you fall in love with Xu Fang?

297
00:24:13,740 --> 00:24:16,380
I fell in love with Xu Fang?

298
00:24:35,340 --> 00:24:38,240
Chi-chi, Chi-chi!

299
00:24:40,380 --> 00:24:43,979
Why are you up so early? Or did you not sleep at all?

300
00:24:46,220 --> 00:24:48,700
I did sleep.

301
00:24:54,660 --> 00:24:56,560
Tell me.

302
00:24:56,560 --> 00:25:01,700
If you dreamed about someone confessing to you,

303
00:25:01,700 --> 00:25:03,499
what does that mean?

304
00:25:03,500 --> 00:25:06,899
- Confess?
- Don't laugh! I'm serious.

305
00:25:06,899 --> 00:25:11,840
I can only say that your dream reflects your desire.

306
00:25:11,840 --> 00:25:14,360
That's impossible.

307
00:25:14,980 --> 00:25:16,680
What's wrong?

308
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:19,400
It's someone you can't accept?

309
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:24,460
Think about this.

310
00:25:24,460 --> 00:25:28,459
If that person kissed someone else, would you be upset?

311
00:25:28,459 --> 00:25:30,580
Close your eyes and think about it.

312
00:25:47,780 --> 00:25:49,600
No way, no way!

313
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:53,099
There's no way that's happening.

314
00:25:53,099 --> 00:25:55,300
Who did you dream of?

315
00:25:57,040 --> 00:26:00,180
Xu Fang.

316
00:26:01,980 --> 00:26:05,320
You finally understand your heart.

317
00:26:11,500 --> 00:26:16,500
But, does he like me though?

318
00:26:26,560 --> 00:26:29,459
- Senior Ye.
- Hello, Chi-chi.

319
00:26:29,459 --> 00:26:32,279
A dog just ran away.

320
00:26:32,279 --> 00:26:35,539
Where are you? I'll come over immediately.

321
00:26:36,460 --> 00:26:39,379
- What's wrong? Going to find Xu Fang?
- Going to find a dog.

322
00:26:39,379 --> 00:26:41,859
- Slow down!
- I'm going.

323
00:26:41,859 --> 00:26:43,580
Take your time!

324
00:26:43,580 --> 00:26:46,479
Why is it so noisy? I'm still sleeping.

325
00:26:46,479 --> 00:26:50,040
I... I-I had a nightmare.

326
00:26:50,580 --> 00:26:52,920
Can you be quiet?

327
00:26:56,840 --> 00:27:00,860
- Can you find me?
- I see you.

328
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:05,859
- How did you lose him?
- I took a walk with Harry.

329
00:27:05,859 --> 00:27:10,359
I tied the leash on a bench, after I bent to tie my shoes and looked up, he was gone.

330
00:27:10,359 --> 00:27:13,559
You go that way, I'll go this way; call me if you find him!

331
00:27:13,559 --> 00:27:15,140
Alright.

332
00:27:17,180 --> 00:27:19,779
Harry, Harry.

333
00:27:19,779 --> 00:27:23,539
Excuse me! Did you see a big dog, about this height.

334
00:27:23,539 --> 00:27:25,699
- I didn't.
- Thank you.

335
00:27:25,699 --> 00:27:27,420
Harry.

336
00:27:28,120 --> 00:27:32,879
Excuse me! Did you see a big dog with white fur?

337
00:27:32,879 --> 00:27:35,399
- We didn't.
- No.
- Thank you.

338
00:27:35,399 --> 00:27:37,280
Harry!

339
00:27:39,840 --> 00:27:41,660
Harry!

340
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:46,480
Harry!

341
00:27:47,180 --> 00:27:48,980
Harry!

342
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:54,139
- You found him?
- I found him.

343
00:27:54,139 --> 00:27:56,899
That's great! I'll wait for you at the place I met you just now.

344
00:27:56,899 --> 00:27:58,420
All right.

345
00:28:31,780 --> 00:28:34,720
Fang Fang! Fang Fang!

346
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:38,200
Lin Xichi! Calm down.

347
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:41,479
Such a large dog won't get lost easily; take the umbrella first.

348
00:28:41,479 --> 00:28:44,479
You look for him there; I'll go this way.

349
00:28:44,479 --> 00:28:46,900
Take the umbrella!

350
00:28:46,900 --> 00:28:48,759
Are you stupid?

351
00:28:48,759 --> 00:28:52,059
You crossed the road without looking, what if the car hit you?

352
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:54,740
Xu Fang.

353
00:28:56,940 --> 00:28:59,080
Tell me!

354
00:28:59,080 --> 00:29:04,120
Is there no relationship that will never change in this world?

355
00:29:04,780 --> 00:29:07,640
Everyone will be separated at some point.

356
00:29:28,220 --> 00:29:30,660
Chi-chi, what's wrong?

357
00:29:30,660 --> 00:29:33,220
No... Nothing!

358
00:29:33,220 --> 00:29:37,580
You haven't been yourself since you came back after the holidays.

359
00:29:40,640 --> 00:29:43,000
You... Are you alright?

360
00:29:47,780 --> 00:29:52,160
Actually, I have something to tell you.

361
00:29:53,370 --> 00:29:57,679
We are so close, you can just tell me at any time. Right?

362
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,860
I like you.

363
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:06,300
I like that you're blunt.

364
00:30:06,300 --> 00:30:09,280
I like your courage, mischief,

365
00:30:09,280 --> 00:30:11,379
and your weakness.

366
00:30:11,379 --> 00:30:14,900
I liked it even more when you wore a white dress for me.

367
00:30:15,660 --> 00:30:18,180
I looked ugly in that white dress.

368
00:30:18,180 --> 00:30:20,460
No, I thought you looked beautiful.

369
00:30:25,440 --> 00:30:27,600
Senior, I'm sorry.

370
00:30:27,600 --> 00:30:30,620
I think that you are excellent

371
00:30:30,620 --> 00:30:33,320
and you have always been a role model to me.

372
00:30:33,320 --> 00:30:38,460
My life in Rong City is different because of you.

373
00:30:39,620 --> 00:30:41,660
But

374
00:30:43,140 --> 00:30:45,310
I realized recently that

375
00:30:45,310 --> 00:30:48,700
there's someone very important to me.

376
00:30:50,680 --> 00:30:54,380
I... I already have someone I like.

377
00:30:57,440 --> 00:30:59,980
Is it Xu Fang?

378
00:31:04,320 --> 00:31:05,899
Senior, thank you.

379
00:31:05,900 --> 00:31:09,739
If it bothers you, I'll leave the pet shop immediately.

380
00:31:09,740 --> 00:31:12,079
No, no, no! You don't have to.

381
00:31:12,079 --> 00:31:15,319
They are unrelated and you love animals.

382
00:31:15,319 --> 00:31:18,420
You even remember all the dogs' name.

383
00:31:18,420 --> 00:31:21,220
Where can I find such a wonderful employee?

384
00:31:26,540 --> 00:31:28,180
Congratulations!

385
00:31:29,120 --> 00:31:32,800
It is very difficult to find out what you want.

386
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:34,970
Then,

387
00:31:34,970 --> 00:31:38,250
we can still be good friends.

388
00:31:38,250 --> 00:31:40,000
Right?

389
00:31:41,120 --> 00:31:42,780
Of course.

390
00:31:43,640 --> 00:31:45,440
Let's go, my wonderful employee!

391
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:47,160
My wonderful boss.

392
00:32:16,460 --> 00:32:20,280
What do you think of Brother Fang?

393
00:32:27,740 --> 00:32:31,380
What do you think of Brother Fang?

394
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:35,300
What do you mean? That's a strange question.

395
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:39,940
I mean, what do you think of him as a person?

396
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:43,800
Bad temper! Always has a long face.

397
00:32:53,020 --> 00:32:56,060
You didn't fall in love with Brother Fang right?

398
00:32:58,180 --> 00:33:00,199
You've known each other for so long.

399
00:33:00,199 --> 00:33:03,479
How could it happen suddenly, if you never liked him before?

400
00:33:03,479 --> 00:33:05,359
You're at the age where love blooms,

401
00:33:05,359 --> 00:33:08,580
so you might have mistaken your relationship with him for love.

402
00:33:12,760 --> 00:33:16,080
Tell me then, how will I know if I like him?

403
00:33:19,940 --> 00:33:23,400
Does your heart beat faster when you see him?

404
00:33:30,320 --> 00:33:32,680
It does when he's close to me.

405
00:33:33,860 --> 00:33:37,180
Do you feel happy when you see him?

406
00:33:41,520 --> 00:33:43,020
Yes.

407
00:33:43,020 --> 00:33:47,740
Are you in a bad mood when he's with another girl?

408
00:33:50,440 --> 00:33:52,480
Of course!

409
00:33:53,180 --> 00:33:55,740
Do you think he likes you?

410
00:33:56,380 --> 00:34:01,260
What does it feel like to like a fool?

411
00:34:05,340 --> 00:34:08,240
Do you think I'm a big fool?

412
00:34:09,280 --> 00:34:11,200
Of course not!

413
00:34:11,200 --> 00:34:13,180
Why did you ask?

414
00:34:16,700 --> 00:34:20,300
