417
00:34:33,900 --> 00:34:37,459
Let me tell you! You must think twice on this.

418
00:34:37,459 --> 00:34:40,979
It's an important matter and it's related to my happiness as well.

419
00:34:40,979 --> 00:34:43,160
I'll have to keep you in check.

420
00:35:13,440 --> 00:35:18,620
Plan to conquer Xu Fang.

421
00:35:22,520 --> 00:35:24,939
