422
00:35:24,939 --> 00:35:27,620
What if someone sees this?

423
00:35:41,120 --> 00:35:46,580
Plan to conquer Fang-fang.

424
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:08,639
First step: Treat him well.

425
00:36:08,639 --> 00:36:12,760
Treat him so well that he gets used to it and can't bear to leave you.

426
00:36:13,280 --> 00:36:17,060
Praise him! Don't stop praising him.

427
00:36:17,060 --> 00:36:20,579
